title: Here come the teletubbies
creator_credit: BBC, Ragdoll Productions, Anne Wood, Vic Finch and David G. Hillier
brief_description: Teletubbies is a TV show that originated on the BBC and has proven to be especially popular among younger children. Tinky Winky, Dipsy, Laa-Laa and Po live in a magical land where television comes from, a land where anything can happen, and usually does. In this video, kids will find out how many things can be put in Tinky Winky’s bag and who spilled the Tubby custard.
